cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use these skills, please cite them as below."
title: "apostle-skills: exacting Agent Skills for serious thinking, reading, research, translation, and prose editing"
abstract: >-
  A line of nine exacting Agent Skills for serious thinking, reading,
  research, translation, and prose editing. It comprises a collaboration
  constitution (apostle-constitutio), an English and Chinese prose editor
  (apostle-antislop), a pre-draft nonfiction research method
  (apostle-article-research), a deep-reading protocol (apostle-opus-reading),
  three method-transplant satellites carrying verbatim French and Japanese kernels
  (apostle-opusmethodology-foucault-archaeology,
  apostle-opusmethodology-foucault-society-defended,
  apostle-opusmethodology-karatani-origins), a low-variance literary and
  academic translation workflow (apostle-translation), and a long-horizon
  artifacts-and-loops protocol for durable multi-stage, multi-agent work
  (apostle-artifacts-loops). Published by KL9 and Luciole Studio.
